org.cornutum.tcases.ant

Class TcasesTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tools.ant.ProjectComponent
      • org.apache.tools.ant.Task
        • org.cornutum.tcases.ant.TcasesTask
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class TcasesTask
extends org.apache.tools.ant.Task
    Defines an Ant task for Tcases. The properties of this class define the attributes of the task. For example, the setInputDef method defines a task attribute named "inputDef". For a detailed description of these properties, see TcasesCommand.Options.

    To define a transform parameter (see the -p option), use a nested <param> element.
